          </p>
          <div class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-2xl bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 mb-8 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
            <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-200 font-medium">
