            Become a Member
          </a>
          <a href="https://discord.com/invite/qkmh9MgVMT" 
             target="_blank"
             rel="noopener noreferrer"
             class="group inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium rounded-full text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-accent/80 to-purple-600/80 hover:from-accent hover:to-purple-600 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-xl hover:shadow-accent/30 transition-all duration-300 gap-2 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5"
